name: sucker-punch
flavor_text: This move enables the user to attack first. This move fails if the target is not readying an attack.
effect_text_extend:
Inflicts regular damage.  If the target has not selected a damaging move this turn, or if the target has already acted this turn, this move will fail.

This move is not affected by iron fist.
effect_text_simple: Only works if the target is about to use a damaging move.
